hadiths[298]{hadithnumber,text}:
267,"Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik mudd (pani) sey wuzu aur eik saa ( pani) sey ghusl kar liya kartey they."
268,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik mudd (pani) sey wuzu aur eik saa (pani ) sey ghusl farmatey they."
269,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik Mudd (pani ) sey wuzu aur eik saa ( pani) sey ghusl farmatey they.
270,"Hazrat Aqeel bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wuzu key liye eik mud (pani) aur ghusl key liye eik saa (pani) kafi hai. eik aadmi ney kaha : hamarey liye to kafi nahin hota. Hazrat Aqeel (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : in ko to kafi hota tha jo tujh sey afzal they aur unkey baal bhi tujh sey ziyada they, yani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)."
271,"Hazrat Usama bin Umer Hazli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala pakizgi key baghair namaz qubul nahin farmata, aur khayanat key maal mein sey (diya huwa) sadqa qubul nahin farmata. Imam Ibne-Maja ney eik teesri sanad yani abu-Bakar bin abi Sheeba ki sanad sey mazkura hadees ki tarah bayan ki."
272,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala paakizgi key baghair namaz qubul nahin farmata aur khayanat key maal mein sey sadqa qubul nahin farmata."
273,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : Allah Taala paakizgi key baghair namaz qubul nahin farmata aur khayanat key maal mein sey sadqa qubul nahin farmata."
274,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala paakizgi key baghair namaz qubul nahin farmata aur khayanat key maal mein sey sadqa qubul nahin farmata."
275,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz ki kunji, paakizgi hai aur namaz ki Tehreem (is mein paabandiyaan laganey wali chiz) takbir hai aur namaz ki tahleel (is mein paabandiyaan khatam karney wali chiz) salam hai."
276,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz ki kunji, paakizgi hai aur namaz ki Tehreem (is mein paabandiyan laganey waliy chiz) takbir hai, aur namaz ki tahleel (is mein paabandiyaan khatam karney waley chiz) salam hai."
277,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sidhi raah par qaaim raho aur tum (haq ke mutabiq) qaaim nahin reh sako gey, aur tumhen malum hona chahiye ke tumhara behtareen amal namaz hai aur wuzu ki hifazat momin hi karta hai."
278,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sidhi raah par qaaim raho , aur tum (haq ke mutabiq) qaaim nahin reh sako gey, aur tumhen malum hona chahiye ke tumhara afzal amal namaz hai aur wuzu ki hifazat momin hi karta hai."
279,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey marfooan riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sidhi raah par qaaim raho aur kitna achchha ho agar tum qaaim reh sako, aur tumhara behtareen amal namaz hai aur wuzu ki hifazat momin hi karta hai."
280,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pura (achchhi tarah) wuzu karna nisf (aadha) eman hai aur Alhamdulillah sey (aamal ka) tarazu bhar jata hai aur tasbih aur takbir sey aasman aur zamin pur ho jatey hain, namaz Noor hai, zakat daleel hai, sabr roshni hai, Quran terey haq mein ya terey khilaf eik hujjat hai, har shakhs subah ko apney aap ko farokht karta hai, khud ko azad kar leta hai ya tabah kar leta hai."
281,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs jab wuzu karta hai aur achchhi tarah (khoob sanwaar kar) wuzu karta hai, phir masjid mein aata hai, usey namaz key ilawa koi aur maqsad ghar sey nahin nikaalta, (aisa shakhs) jo qadam bhi uthata hai, uskey badley Allah Taala uska eik darja buland farmata hai aur eik gunah maaf karta hai. (usey musalsal ye sawab milta rehta hai) yahan tak key wo masjid mein dakhil ho jata hai."
282,"Hazrat Abdullah Sunabihi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs wuzu karta hai aur (wuzu kartey huye) kulli karta aur naak mein pani daalta hai to uskey munh aur naak sey gunah nikal jatey hain, phir jab chehra dhota hai to uskey chehrey sey gunah nikal jatey hain yahan tak key uski aakhon key papoton sey bhi nikal jatey hain. phir jab apney haath dhota hai to uskey haathon sey gunah nikal jatey hain, phir jab sar ka masah karta hai to uskey sar sey gunah nikal jatey hain, yahan tak key kanon mein sey bhi nikal jatey hain. phir jab apney paon dhota hai to uskey paon sey gunah nikal jatey hain. hattaa key paon key naakhunon key nichey sey bhi nikal jatey hain phir uski namaz aur uska masjid ki taraf chal kar jana mazeed (darjaat mein bulandi ka baais) hota hai."
283,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab banda wuzu karta hai aur apney haath dhota hai to uskey haathon sey gunah gir jatey hain, phir jab apna chehra dhota hai to uskey chehrey sey gunah gir jatey hain. phir jab apney bazu dhota hai aur apney sar ka masah karta hai to uskey baazuon aur sar sey gunah gir jatey hain. phir jab apney paon dhota hai to uskey paon sey gunah gir jatey hain."
284,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha (poochha) gaya : aap ney apni ummat key jin afrad ko nahin dekha, unhein (qiyamat key din) kis tarah pahchaaneingey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo wuzu key nishaanaat sey panj-kaliyan, chitkabrey hongey. Imam Ibne-Maja key shagrid Abu-Hasan Qataan ney Abu Hatim key wastey sey bhi mazkura riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
285,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Humran (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) ko maqame  maqaaide  par bethey dekha, (wahan) unhoney pani mangwaya kar wuzu kiya, phir farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi maqam par bethey dekha tha, aap ney bhi isi tarah ka wuzu kiya tha jis tarah mainey ye wuzu kiya hai, phir farmaya tha : jo shakhs merey is wuzu jaisa wuzu kerega, uskey tamam pichhley gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey . aur (iskey baad) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye bhi farmaya : aur maghroor na ho jana. (ya tum dhoka na khana.) Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Hisham bin Ammar key wastey sey bhi mazkura riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
286,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko namaze tahajjud key liye bedaar hotey they to miswak key sath apna munh saaf kartey they."
287,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye baat na hoti ke main apni ummat ko mashaqqat mein dal dunga to main unhein har namaz key waqt miswak karney ka hukm deta.
288,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko do-do rakat namaz padhtey rehtey they, phir (har do rakat sey) farigh ho kar miswak kartey they."
289,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : miswak kiya karo kyonkey miswak munh saaf karney wali hai aur Allah Taala ko khush karney wali hai. Jibril (Alaihissalam) jab bhi merey paas aaye, miswak ki takeed zarur ki. yahan tak key mujhey khof mehsus huwa ke mujh par aur meri ummat par wo (miswaak) farz kar di jaeygi. aur agar mujhey ummat par mashaqqat ka khof na hota to main isey un par farz kar deta. main to is qadr miswak karta hun ke mujhey khatra mehsus hota hai ke munh ka aglaa hissa chheel dalunga."
290,"Hazrat Shureh bin Hani (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey arz kiya : mujhey ye bataaiye ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ( bahar sey) aap key paas aatey to sab sey pehley kya kartey they? Ummul-momenin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghar mein tashrif latey to sab sey pehley miswak kartey they."
291,"Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : tumharey munh Quran key raastey hain, lihaza inhein miswak key zariey sey paak-saaf rakha karo."
292,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : fitrat paanch cheezen hain, ya farmaya : paanch cheezen fitrat mein sey hain : khatna, (zer naaf baalon ki safai key liye) lohey ki chiz istimal karna, nakhun taraashnaa, baghlon key baal ukhadna aur munchhein kaatnaa."
293,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : das cheezen fitrat sey hain : munchhein kaatnaa, daadhi badhaanaa, miswak karna, (dorane wuzu) naak mein pani dalna, nakhun taraashnaa, ungliyon key jod dhonaa, baghlon key baal ukhaadna, zere naaf baal mundna aur pani istimal karna, yani istinja karna. (hadees key eik Raavi) Hazrat Musab (Rahimahullah) ney (hadees riwayat kartey huye) farmaya : main daswein chiz bhool gaya hun, shayad kulli karna ho."
294,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye cheezen fitrat sey hain : kulli karna , naak mein pani dalna , miswak karna , munchhein kaatna , nakhun kaatna , baghlon key baal ukhaadna, (zere naaf safai key liye) lohey ki chiz istimal karna , ungliyon key jod dhona , chheentey maarna aur khatna karna. Imam Ibne-Maja ney ye riwayat Hammad bin Salma key doosrey shagrid Affaan bin Muslim ki sanad sey bhi isi tarah bayan ki hai."
295,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : munchhein kaatney, zere naaf baal moondney, baghlon key baal ukhaadney aur nakhun kaatney key liye hamarey liye ye had muqarrar ki gaee hai ke inhein chaalis raaton sey ziyada na choden."
296,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye baitul-khalaa (shetanon key) hazir honey ki jaghen hain. chunanche jab tum mein sey koi (baitul-khalaa mein) dakhil ho, to usey yun kehna chahiye : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّى أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنَ الْخُبُثِ وَالْخَبَائِثِ )''aey Allah ! main teri panah mein aata hun napak jinnon aur napak Jinniyon sey.'' Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney yehi riwayat apney doosrey do ustaad Jameel bin Hasan Ataki aur Harun bin Is-haq ki sanadon sey bhi ye riwayat isi tarah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan ki hai."
297,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bani Adam (insanon) key pardey key aaza aur jinnon ki nazron key darmiyan ye chiz parda bin jati hai ke jab koi baitul-khalaa mein dakhil ho to (بِسْمِ اللہ) kahey."
298,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khalaa mein dakhil hotey to kehtey they : ( أَعُوذُ بِاللہ مِنَ الْخُبُثِ وَالْخَبَائِثِ )'mein napaak jinnon aur napaak jinniyon sey Allah ki panah mein aata hun.''
299,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi ko is baat sey aajiz nahin hona chahiye ke baitul-khalaa mein dakhil hotey waqt yun keh ley : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنَ الرِّجْسِ النَّجِسِ الْخَبِيثِ الْمُخْبِثِ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّجِيمِ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah mein aata hun gandey, paleed, napaak, gandey kaam sikhaaney waley mardud shetan sey. Abu Hatim ney ibne-Abi Maryam sey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki lekin usney apni riwayat mein (مِنَ الرِّجْسِ النَّجَسِ ) key alfaz bayan nahin kiye balke sirf (مِنَ الْخَبِيثِ الْمُخْبِثِ ) key alfaz bayan kiye hain. Abu Hatim ney ibne-Abi Maryam sey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki lekin usney apni riwayat mein (مِنَ الرِّجْسِ النَّجَسِ) key alfaz bayan nahin kiye balke sirf (مِنَ الْخَبِيثِ الْمُخْبِثِ ) key alfaz bayan kiye hain."
300,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khalaa sey bahar aatey they to farmatey they : (غُفْرَانَکَ) ''aey Allah ! main teri bakhshish ka talabgar hun.'' Abu-Ghassaan An Nehdi ney bhi Israel sey isi (Yahya bin abi bakeer) ki jaisi riwayat bayan ki."
301,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khalaa sey bahar tashrif latey to farmatey : ( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِى أَذْهَبَ عَنِّى الأَذَى وَعَافَانِى )''Allah ka shukar hai jisney mujh sey najasat (ya takleef deh chiz) ko door kar diya aur mujhey aafiyat bakhshi.''"
302,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney tamam oqaat mein Allah ka zikr farmaya kartey they.
303,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-khalaa mein dakhil hotey to angoothi utaar detey they.
304,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs apney ghusl-khaney mein hergiz peshab na karey, kyonkey ziyada tar waswasey isi wajeh sey paida hotey hain. Janab Ali bin Muhammad Tanaafusi (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye hukm aisey (kachchey) ghusl khaanon key barey mein hai jinka pani gadhey mein jama hota hai. aaj kal ye hukm nahin. chunkey ab log ghusl khaanon ki taamir mein choonaa, qalaee aur taarkol istimal kartey hain, (isliye pukhta farsh par pani nahin theharta aur aisi deewaron mein bhi jazb nahin hota) lihaza jab aadmi peshab kar key us jagah pani baha dey to koi harj nahin."
305,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kuchh logon key kuda-karkat phainkney ki jagah pahunchey aur wahan khadey ho kar peshab kiya.
306,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi qom ki kuda-karkat phainkney ki jagah pahunchey aur khadey ho kar peshab kiya. Imam Shoba key ustaad Aasim bayan kartey hain ke Aamash is hadees ko Abu-Waeil key wastey sey Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, un sey bhool ho gaee hai. (ke asal mein ye hadees Mughira bin Shoba ki hai, Aamash ney ghalati sey Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam ley diya hai.) Imam Shoba kehtey hain ke mainey Mansoor sey puchha to unhoney mujhey Abu-Waeil key wastey sey Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kiya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi qom ki kudr-karkat phainkney ki jagah pahunchey aur khadey ho kar peshab kiya."
307,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jo shakhs tumhen ye baat bataey ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey ho kar peshab kiya, uski tasdeeq na karna, mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (hamesha) beth kar peshab kartey dekha hai."
308,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey khadey ho kar peshab kartey dekha to farmaya : umr ! khadey ho kar peshab na karo. (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ) uskey baad mainey kabhi khadey ho kar peshab nahin kiya."
309,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey ho kar peshab karney sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Ibne-Maja ney apney ustaad Ahmed bin Abdur-Rehman Makhzoomi key wastey sey hadees Aaisha key barey mein Hazrat Sufiyan Sory sey riwayat kiya hai ke unhoney farmaya : is masley mein mardon ko ziyada maloomat ho sakti hain. yani Imam Sufiyan Sory ney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key farman : mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (hamesha) beth kar peshab kartey dekha hai. par Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees (hadees : 305) ko tarjeeh di hai. Ahmed bin Abdur-Rehman Makhzoomi ney farmaya : Arbon mein khadey ho kar peshab karney ka riwaaj tha. isliye Abdur-Rehman bin Hasna ki hadees mein ye alfaz hain : (yahudiyon ney kaha) ye to beth kar peshab kartey hain jis tarah aurten peshab kiya karti hain."
310,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : jab koi shakhs peshab karey to usey chahiye ke uzu-khaas ko daain haath sey na chhuey aur na daain haath sey istinja kerey. Imam Ibne-Maja ney Imam Auzaai (Rahimahullah) key doosrey shagrid Waleed bin Muslim ki sanad sey bhi ye hadees isi tarah bayan ki.
311,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : mainey na kabhi gaanaa gaaya, na jhoot bola, aur na uzue-khaas ko daain haath sey chhua, jab sey mainey is (haath) sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki."
312,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs jab istinja karey to daain haath sey istinja na kerey. usey apney baaein hath sey istinja karna chahiye."
313,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tumharey liye is tarah hun jis tarah aulad key liye baap hota hai. (isliye) main tumhen (ba-zahir maamuli samajhey janey waley umoor ki bhi) taalim deta hun. jab tum qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) key liye jao to qibley ki taraf munh na karo aur uski taraf peeth bhi na karo. aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen dheley istimal karney ka hukm diya, leed aur haddi istimal karney sey mana farmaya, aur daain haath sey istinja karney sey mana farmaya."
314,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) key liye tashrif ley gaey aur farmaya : mujhey teen patthar la do. main do pathar aur eik leed ley aaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dono patthar ley liye aur leed phenk di aur farmaya. ye napaak hai.
315,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : istinje mein teen patthar (istimal) hotey hain, in mein gobar, leed na ho."
316,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke baaz mushrekin unka mazaq udaney lagey, eik mushrik ney kaha : main dekhta hun ke tumhara sathi (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) tumhen sab kuchh sikhata hai yahan tak key pakhana karna bhi (sikhata hai) Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : haan, aap ney hamein hukm diya hai ke hum (peshaab-paakhaane key liye)  qibley ki taraf munh na keren, aur daain haath sey istinja na keren, aur teen pattharon sey kam istimal na keren, un mein leed ya haddi shamil na ho."
317,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz Zubaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : sab sey pehley mainey hi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : tum mein sey koi qibley ki taraf munh kar key peshab na kerey. aur sab sey pehley mainey hi logon ko ye hadees sunai."
318,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) key liye janey waley ko qibley ki taraf munh karney sey mana kiya aur farmaya : mashriq ya maghrib ki taraf munh kiya karo."
319,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Abu-Ma'aqil Asadi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba hain, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney pakhana peshab kartey waqt dono qiblon (Kaaba aur Baitul-Maqdis) ki taraf munh karney sey hamen mana farmaya."
320,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key barey mein gawahi di ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney peshab ya pakhane key waqt qibley ki taraf munh karney sey mana farmaya."
321,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey ho kar pani peeney aur qibley ki taraf munh kar key peshab karney sey mana farmaya."
322,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : kuchh log kehtey hain jab tum qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) key liye betho to tumhara chehra qibley ki taraf nahin hona chahiye. main eik din apney ghar ki chhat par chadha to mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh kiye huye do kachchi inton par bethey dekha. ye riwayat Yazeed bin Harun ki hai."
323,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko baitul-khalaa mein qibley ki taraf munh kar key bethey huye dekha. (hadees ki sanad main eik Raavi)  Esa Khayyaat bayan kartey hain ke mainey Imam Shaaby sey is hadees key mutalliq daryaft kiya to unhoney farmaya : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney bhi sach kaha aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi sach kaha. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ka matlab hai ke sehra (aur khuley maidan) mein qibley ki taraf munh ya peeth kar key na bethey, aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ki hadees ka matlab ye hai ke baitul-khalaa key andar qibley ka khayal rakhna zaruri nahin, wahan tum jidhar chaho munh kar saktey ho. Abu Hatim ney Ubedullah bin Musa sey isi (Muhammad bin Yahya) ki jaisi riwayat bayan ki."
324,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein zikr huwa ke kuchh log baitul-khalaa mein qibley ki taraf munh karna makrooh samajhtey hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera khayal hai ke wo amali tor par bhi ijtinab kartey (bachte) hongey. meri baitul-khalaa ka rukh qibley ki taraf kar do. Abul-Hasan Al-Qattan ney kaha : Yahya bin Abdaka ney Abdul-Azeez bin Mughira sey, unhoney Khalid Hazzaa sey, unhoney Khalid bin Abi Salat sey sabiqa riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
325,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen peshab kartey waqt qibley ki taraf munh karney sey mana farmaya tha. phir mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wafat sey eik saal pehley us taraf munh kartey dekha."
326,"Hazrat Esa bin Yazdaad Yamaani apney walid sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs peshab karey to uzu ko teen baar soont ley (zor sey daba kar kheenchey taake uskey andar jo qatraat hain, wo nikal jaaeyn). Abul-Hasan bin Salma ney kaha ke Ali bin Abdul-Azeez ney Abu Nuaim sey Zamaa key wastey sey isi (Muhammad bin Yahya) ki jaisi riwayat bayan ki."
327,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peshab key liye (bahir) tashrif ley gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) pani ley kar aap key peechhey chaley to aap ney farmaya : umr ye kya hai?  unhoney kaha pani. aap ney farmaya : mujhey ye hukm nahin diya gaya ke jab bhi peshab karun, to wuzu bhi karun. agar main aisa karunga to ye (lazimi) sunnat bin jaaeygi."
328,"Abu-Saeed Hameeri sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) wo hadeesen bayan kiya kartey they jo doosrey Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney nahin suni hoti thin, aur jo hadisein dusron ney suni hoti thin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) unhein bayan nahin kartey they. un ki bayan karda koi hadees Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) ko malum hui to unhoney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman nahin suna. mumkin hai Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) (key ye hadees bayan kerney) ki wajeh sey tum log ghalat fehmi mein mubtala ho jao. ye baat Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) tak bhi pahunch gaee. (eik moqe par) un ki aapas mein mulaqat hui to Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aey Abdullah bin Amr ! Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansub kar key jhoot bolnaa munafiqat hai. jo shakhs aisi baat kerega, khud gunah gaar hoga. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshade Mubarak suna hai : lanat ka sabab ban'ney waley teen kamon sey ijtinab karo (bacho), yani ghaat par, saye mein aur raastey key darmiyan qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) karney sey (parhez karo)."
329,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raastey key darmiyan (raat ko aaram karney aur soney key liye ( na thehrao , aur wahan namaz na padho kyon ye saanpon aur darindon ka thikana hai, aur wahan qazaey-hajat na karo kyonkey ye lanat ka baais hai."
330,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney raastey mein namaz padhney sey ya qazaey-hajat karney sey ya peshab karney sey mana farmaya hai.
331,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab qazaey-hajat key liye jatey to door tashrif ley jatey they."
332,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. aap qazaey-hajat key liye door tashrif ley gaey, phir wapis aa kar wuzu key liye pani talab farmaya aur wuzu kya."
333,"Hazrat Yala bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab qazaey-hajat key liye jatey to door tashrif ley jatey they."
334,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abu Qiraad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj kya. ( raastey mein) aap qazaey-hajat key liye gaey to ( logon sey) door tashrif ley gaey ."
335,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik safar mein rawana huye .) safar key doran mein) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us waqt tak qazaey-hajat nahin kartey they jab tak ke nazron sey ojhal na ho jatey aur kisi ko nazar na aatey ."
336,Hazrat Bilal bin Haris Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab qazaey-hajat key liye jatey to door chaley jatey.
337,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo dheley istimal karey wo taaq tadaad mein istimal kerey. jisney aisa kya to achcha kya. jisney na kya to koi harj nahin . jisney ( daanton mein) Khilal istimal kya to ( khaney key jo zarrey waghera niklen unhein) phenk dey aur jo kuch zaban key zariey sey (daanton key darmiyan sey) nikal aaye usey nigal ley. jisney is tarah kya to achcha kya, jisney na kya to koi harj nahin . jo shakhs qazaey-hajat key liye jaey usey chahiye ke parda kerey. agar ret ki dheri key siwa koi ot na miley to (mazeed ret jama kar key) is mein izafa kar ley (taake munasib had tak pardey key qabil ho jaey) kyonkey shetan insan ki peeth sey chhed chhaad karta hai. jisney aisa kya to achcha kya. jisney na kya to koi harj nahin ."
338,usi hadees ki eik riwayat mein ye izafa hai : jo surma lagaey to taaq tadaad mein lagaey . jisney aisa kya to achcha kya. jisney na kya to koi harj nahin . aur jo shakhs zaban key zariey sey (daanton key darmiyan sey) kuch nikaley to usey chahiye ke nigal ley .
339,"Hazrat Yala bin Murra (Raziallahu anhuma) apney walid (Murra bin Wahab saqafii) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : main eik safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. aap ney qazaey-hajat ka irada kya to mujh sey farmaya : khajoor key un do chhotey paudon key paas ja kar unhein kaho : Allah key Rasool tumhen hukm detey hain ke aapas mein mil jao . chunanche wo mil gaey . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey zariey sey parda farma kar hajat puri ki, phir mujh sey farmaya : unkey paas ja kar kaho : tum mein sey har pauda apni apni jagah wapis chala jaey . mainey unhein kaha to wo apni apni jagah wapis chaley gaey ."
340,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qazaey-hajat key moqey par kisi tiley ya khajuron key jhund ki aad lena ziyada pasand farmatey they."
341,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raastey sey hat kar ghaati ki taraf chaley gaey aur (wahan ja kar) peshab kya. jab aap ney peshab kya to main aap key qarib (munh dusri taraf kar key khada) tha taake aap ki pusht zahir na ho."
342,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qazaey-hajat kartey waqt do aadmi baaten na karen ke har eik ki nazar apney sathi key pardey key aaza par pad rahi ho. Allah Taala us (ghalat kaam) sey sakht naraz hota hai.' Muhammad bin Yahya (mazkoora riwayat jab) ikrima bin Ammar key (doosrey) shagrid Silm bin Ibrahim al-Warraq sey bayan kartey hain to Raavi ka naam (Hilal bin Ayaaz ki bajaey) Ayaaz bin Hilal bayan kartey hain, aur kehtey hain ke yehi durust aur sahih hai. Muhammad bin Humed (mazkoora riwayat jab) ikrima bin Ammar key (teesrey) shagrid Sufiyan Sory sey bayan kartey hain to Raavi ka naam ( Hilal bin ayaaz aur ayaaz bin Hilal ki bajaey) ayaaz bin Abdullah bayan kartey hain."
343,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney thehrey huye pani mein peshab karney sey mana farmaya.
344,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs thehrey huye pani mein hergiz peshab na kerey."
345,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs thehrey huye pani mein hergiz peshab na kerey."
346,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Hasna (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ghar sey) bahar hamarey paas tashrif laye aur aap key haath main eik dhaal thi.) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko peshab ki hajat mehsus hui to (usey) zamin par rakha aur uski taraf rukh kar key beth kar peshab kya. kisi ney kaha : un sahab ko dekho is tarah peshab kartey hain jis tarah aurat kya karti hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uski baat sun li . chunanche farmaya : tujh par afsos ! kya tujhey malum nahin ke Bani-Israel key us aadmi key sath kya huwa? un logon ko jab ( kapdey waghera ko) peshab lag jata to qenchiyon sey kaat diya kartey they (kyonkey un ki shariyat mein yehi hukm tha) usney unhein us sey mana kar diya to usey qabr mein azab diya gaya. Imam Ibne-Maja ney Aamash key doosrey shagrid Ubedullah bin Musa sey usi (abu-Muaawia) ki misl riwayat bayan ki.
347,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do naee qabron key paas sey guzrey to farmaya : un dono ( aadmiyon) ko azab ho raha hai aur kisi badi wajeh sey azab nahin ho raha . un mein sey eik to apney peshab sey nahin bachta tha aur doosra chughal-khori ka aadi tha."
348,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : azabe-qabr ziyada tar peshab ( sey ehtiyat na kerney) ki wajeh sey hota hai."
349,Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do qabron key paas sey guzrey to farmaya : un do shakhson ko azab ho raha hai. aur azab bhi kisi badey kaam ki wajeh sey nahin ho raha . eik ko to peshab ki wajeh sey azab ho raha hai aur doosrey ko gheebat ki saza mil rahi hai.'
350,"Hazrat Muhajir bin Qanfaz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa jabke aap wuzu kar rahey they. mainey salam kaha to aap ney jawab na diya . jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wuzu sey farigh huye to farmaya : mainey salam ka jawab sirf us wajeh sey nahin diya tha ke main be wuzu tha., 'Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Saeed bin abi Aruba key doosrey shagrid al-Ansari sey bhi ye riwayat isi tarah bayan ki hai."
351,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peshab kar rahey they ke eik aadmi paas sey guzraa, usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par salam kya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jawab na diya. jab aap farigh huye to zamin par dono haath maar kar tayammum kya, phir uskey salam ka jawab diya."
352,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peshab kar rahey they ke eik aadmi paas sey guzra to usney salam kaha . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : jab tum mujhey us haalat mein dekho to salam na kaha karo . agar tum aisa karogey to main tumhen jawab nahin dunga.
353,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peshab kar rahey they ke eik aadmi paas sey guzraa. usney salam kaha to aap ney jawab na diya ."
354,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey nahin dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kabhi baitul-khala sey tashrif laye hon aur pani istimal na kya ho."
355,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari, Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah aur Hazrat Anas bin Malik Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai ke jab ye aayat nazil hui : ( فِيهِ رِجَالٌ يُحِبُّونَ أَنْ يَتَطَهَّرُوا وَاللَّهُ يُحِبُّ الْمُطَّهِّرِينَ )' us masjid mein aisey aadmi ( namaz padhtey) hain jo pak rehna pasand kartey hain aur Allah bhi pak rehney walon ko pasand farmata hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey ansaar ki jamaat! Allah Taala ney tumhari safai pasandi ki tareef ki hai. tumhari safai kaisi hoti hai? unhoney arz kya : hum namaz key liye wuzu kartey hain, janabat sey ghusl kartey hain aur pani sey istinja kartey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : yehi baat hai. us ko ikhtiyar kiye rakhna ."
356,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (istinja kartey waqt) pusht teen baar dhotey they. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : hamney us amal ko ikhtiyar kya to usey ilaj bhi paya aur pakizgi ka baais bhi. abul-Hasan bin Salma Qataan ney apni sanad sey bhi mazkura riwayat ki tarah bayan kya hai.
357,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aayat mubaraka ( فِيْهِ رِجَالٌ يُّحِبُّوْنَ اَنْ يَّتَطَهَّرُوْا padhi. وَاللّٰهُ يُحِبُّ الْمُطَّهِّرِيْنَ )' us masjid mein aisey aadmi ( namaz padhtey ( hain jo pak rehna pasand kartey hain, aur Allah bhi pak rehney walon ko pasand farmata hai. qubaa walon key barey mein nazil hui hai. farmaya : wo pani sey istinja kartey they, to unkey barey mein ye aayat nazil hui ."
358,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qazaey-hajat ki, phir pital key bartan sey (pani ley kar) istinja kya, phir haath zamin par ragad kar saaf kya. abul-Hasan bin Salma Qataan ney ye hadees shareek key doosrey shagrid Saeed bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) al-Wasti ki sanad sey usi ki misl bayan ki."
359,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah bijli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) darakhton key eik jhund mein dakhil huye aur qazaey-hajat ki. Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) ney pani ka bartan hazir kya, chunanche aap ney us sey istinja farmaya aur haath ko mitti sey ragda."
360,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hukm diya hai ke hum apney mishkeezon ka munh baandh diya karen aur bartanon ko dhank diya karen."
361,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan karti hain ke main raat key waqt Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye teen dhanke huye bartan tayyar rakhti thi. eik bartan aap key wuzu key liye , eik aap key miswak key liye aur eik aap key peeney key liye."
362,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni paakizgi (wuzu waghera) aur apna sadqa jo kisi ko dena hota tha, kisi key supurd nahin kartey they balke ye kaam khud kartey they."
363,"Janab abu-Rizeen (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney peshani par haath maara aur kaha : aey Iraaq walo ! tumhara ye khayal hai ke main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par jhoot bol raha hun? (uska nateeja ye hoga) ke tumhen faeyda hasil ho jaey aur mujhey gunah ho. main gawahi deta hun ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : jab tum mein sey kisi key bartan mein kutaa munh dal dey to usey chahiye ke us (bartan) ko saat baar dhoey."
364,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi key bartan mein kutta pi ley to usey chahiye ke us (bartan) ko saat baar dhoey."
365,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab bartan mein kutta pi ley to usey saat baar dho'o aur aathwein martaba mitti key sath saaf karo.
366,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi key bartan mein kutta pi ley to usey chahiye ke us (bartan) ko saat baar dhoey."
367,"Hazrat Kabsha binte Kaabi (Raziallahu anha) jo Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) key eik betey ki biwi thin, un sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) key liye bartan mein pani dal kar rakha taake wo wuzu kar lein. (itney mein) eik billi aa kar (us sey pani) peeney lagi. Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ney bartan jhuka diya (taake wo aasani sey pani pi ley), (Hazrat Kabsha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya)  main un ki taraf (tajjub sey) dekhney lagi to unhoney farmaya : meri bhatiji ! kya tumhen tajjub ho raha hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye naapak nahin. ye to (har waqt gharon mein) aati jaati rehti hai."
368,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan sey wuzu kar liya kartey they jabke is mein sey pehley billi ney pani piya hota tha."
369,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : billi (key namazi key aagey sey guzarney) sey namaz nahin tootti kyonkey wo ghar ki ashiya (cheezon) mein sey hai.
370,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik zauja (biwi) mohtarma (Raziallahu anha) ney eik tab mein (pani ley kar) ghusl kiya. uskey baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusl ya wuzu karney key liye tashrif laye to unhoney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main junbi (samhog ke baad ki napaak) thi. to (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya :) ,pani napaak nahin hota."
371,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke paak biwiyon Raziallahu anhu mein sey kisi zauja mohtarma ney ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad ka ghusl) kiya. unkey wuzu sey bachey huye pani sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu aur ghusl farma liya.
372,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat bayan ki hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey ghusle-janabat (samhog ke bad ka ghusl) sey bachey huye pani sey ghusl farmaya.
373,Hazrat Hakam bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aurat key wuzu sey bachey huye pani sey aadmi ko wuzu karney sey mana farmaya.
374,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya hai ke aurat key wuzu sey bachey huye pani sey aadmi ghusl karey, ya mard key bachey huye pani sey aurat ghusl kerey. balke (ye hukm diya ke) dono ikhatta shuru kar den. Abu-Adbullah Ibne-Maja (muallif (lekhak) Sunan Ibne-Maja) ney kaha : sahih pehli baat hai. dusri weham hai. Abul-Hasan bin Salma ney kaha, hamein Abu Hatim aur Abu-Usman Mahaaribi ney bayan kiya, un dono ney kaha ke hamein Mualla bin Asad ney saabiq riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
375,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki zauja (biwi) eik hi bartan sey (pani ley ley kar) ghusl kar liya kartey they lekin eik doosrey key bachey huye pani sey ghusl nahin kartey they."
376,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan karti hain ke main aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan sey ghusl kar liya kartey they."
377,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan sey ghusl kar liya kartey they."
378,Hazrat Umme-Haani (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ney eik tab (mein pani ley kar us) sey ghusl kiya jabke us (bartan) mein goondhey huye aatey ka asar tha.
379,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdulla (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki azwaaje mutah'raat (paak biwiyan) eik hi bartan sey ghusl kar liya kartey they."
380,Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan mein sey ghusl kar letey they.
381,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein mard aur aurten eik hi bartan mein sey wuzu kar liya kartey they."
382,"Hazrat Umme Sabiya Zuhaina (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik hi bartan mein sey wuzu kartey huye baaz oqaat mera haath aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath eik sath (bartan mein) padta. Imam abu-Adbullah Ibne-Maja ney farmaya : mainey Muhammad (bin Yahyaa Zahli) sey suna, wo kehtey they, Umme Sabiya, Khaula binte Qais hai. ye baat mainey Abu-Zara'a sey zikr ki to unhoney kaha, Muhammad ney sach kaha."
383,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz key liye wuzu mil kar (ikhattey) kar liya kartey they.
384,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jinnon sey mulaqat wali raat un sey farmaya : kya tumharey paas wuzu ka pani hai? mainey arz kiya : ji nahin, bas chamdey key bartan mein thodi si nabeez hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paak khajuren hain aur paak karney wala pani hai.  phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (usi pani sey) wuzu kar liya. ye riwayat Wakee ki hai."
385,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke jinnon wali raat Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : kya tumharey paas pani hai? unhoney kaha : nahin . lekin mishkize mein nabeez mojud hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paak khajuren hain aur paak karney wala pani hai, mujh par dalo. mainey (nabeez ko) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key haathon par undelaa aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey sath wuzu kiya."
386,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum samandar ka safar kartey hain aur apney sath thoda sa pani ley letey hain. agar hum us sey wuzu kar lein to piyasey reh jaeyngey. (peeney key liye pani nahin rahega) to kya hum samandar key pani sey wuzu kar liya keren? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uska pani paak karney wala aur uska mara huwa janwer halal hai."
387,"Hazrat ibne Farasi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main shikar kiya karta tha aur merey paas eik mashk thi, main is mein pani dal liya karta tha. mainey samandar key pani sey wuzu kiya, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye waqia bayan kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uska pani pak karney wala hai aur uska mara huwa janwer halal hai."
388,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey samandar key pani key barey mein sawal kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : uska pani paak karney wala hai aur uska mara huwa janwer halal hai. (Imam Ibne-Maja key shagrid) Abul-Hasan bin Salma ney Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal key doosrey shagrid Ali bin Hasan Hastajaani sey mazkura baala riwayat ki maanind bayan kiya.
389,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi kaam sey tashrif ley gaey. jab aap wapis aaye to main pani ka bartan ley kar hazir huwa. mainey pani dala to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dono haath dhoey, phir Chehra Mubarak dhoya , phir apney bazu dhoney ka irada kiya to jubba ki aasteenein tang malum huin, chunanche aap ney jubba key nichey sey bazu nikal liye aur unhein dhoya aur mozon par masah kiya, phir hamein namaz padhaai."
390,"Hazrat Rabee binte Muawwiz (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main wuzu ka bartan ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. aap ney farmaya : pani dalo. mainey pani dala to aap ney apna Chehra Mubarak aur dono bazu dhoey. phir naya pani liya aur uskey sath sar key agley aur pichley hissey ka masah kiya aur apney paon ko teen teen baar dhoya."
391,"Hazrat Safwan bin Assaal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey safar aur hazar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu karaney key liye (aap key haathon aur paon par) pani dala."
392,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sahab-zaadi Hazrat Ruqaiya (Raziallahu anha) ki londi Hazrat Umme Aayash‬ (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu karaya karti thi. main khadi hoti thi aur aap bethey hotey they."
393,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs raat ko so kar jaagey to bartan mein apna haath na daley jab tak is par do teen baar pani na dal ley. (haath dho kar pani mein daley) kyonkey usey malum nahin ke raat ko uska haath kahan raha hai.
394,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs neend sey bedaar ho to bartan mein haath na daley yahan tak key haath dho ley."
395,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi neend sey bedaar ho kar wuzu karna chahey to wuzu key pani mein haath na daley jab tak usey dho na ley kyonkey usey malum nahin ke raat ko uska haath kahan raha hai aur na ye malum hai ke usney kis chiz par haath rakha hai.  Abu-Is'haq ney kaha, sahih sanad Jabir an Abi Huraira hai."
396,"Hazrat Haris sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney pani mangwaya , phir pani mein haath dalney sey pehley haath dhoey , phir farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha hai."
397,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is shakhs ka wuzu nahin jo wuzu kartey waqt Allah ka naam nahin leta.
398,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is shakhs ki namaz nahin jis ka wuzu nahin aur uska wuzu nahin jisney is mein Allah ka naam na liya ho."
399,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is shakhs ki namaz nahin jis ka wuzu nahin aur uska wuzu nahin jisney (wuzu kartey waqt) Allah ka naam na liya ho.
400,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is shakhs ki namaz nahin jis ka wuzu nahin aur uska wuzu nahin jisney (wuzu kartey waqt) Allah ka naam na liya ho aur uski namaz nahin jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par durood nahin padhta. aur jo Ansaar sey mohabbat nahin rakhta uski bhi namaz nahin.(Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) Abul-Hasan bin Salma ney Abdul Muhemin bin Abbas key doosrey shagrid Abees bin Marhoom Attaar sey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
401,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wuzu mein ye baat pasand thi ke jab wuzu karen to daain taraf sey shuru karen aur jab kanghi karen to daain taraf sey kanghi karna shuru karen, aur jab joota pahnein to pehley daayan joota pahnein ."
402,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum wuzu karo to daain taraf sey shuru karo. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) abul-Hasan bin Salma ney zuhair key do shagirdon yahyaa bin Saleh aur ibn Nufel sey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki.
403,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik hi chullu sey kulli bhi ki aur naak mein pani bhi dala .
404,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kya, to eik chullu sey teen baar kulli ki aur teen baar naak mein pani dala ."
405,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur wuzu key liye pani talab farmaya : mainey pani hazir kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik chullu sey kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala ."
406,"Hazrat Salma bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : jab to wuzu karey to naak saaf kya kar aur jab (qazaey-hajat key baad) dheley istimal karey to taaq tadaad mein istimal kar ."
407,"Hazrat laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey wuzu key barey mein irshad farmaiye . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wuzu achi tarah pura kar, aur naak mein pani dalney mein mubaalgha kar, siwaye uskey ke to rozey sey ho."
408,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do teen baar achi tarah naak saaf karo ."
409,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs wuzu karey , usey chahiye ke naak jhaadey , aur jo (istinja key liye) dheley istimal kerey. usey chahiye ke taaq tadaad mein istimal kerey."
410,"Hazrat Sabit bin Abi Safiya Samaali sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey Abu-Jafar sey puchha : kya aap ko Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey marvi ye hadees pahunchi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik eik baar (ang dho kar) wuzu kiya? unhoney farmaya : haan, mainey kaha : aur (ye hadees bhi ke) do do baar aur teen teen baar (aaza dho kar wuzu kiya?) unhoney farmaya : haan."
411,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney eik eik chullu ley kar wuzu kya."
412,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey tabuk ki jng key doran mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney eik eik baar (aaza dho kar) wuzu kya."
413,"Hazrat Shaqeeq bin Salma (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Usman aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhuma) ko dekha ke wo teen-teen baar  aaza dho kar) wuzu kartey they aur farmatey they : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wuzu is tarah huwa karta tha. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) Abul-Hasan bin Salma ney kaha : hamein Abu Hatim ney Abu Nuaim sey unhoney Abdur-Rehman bin Sabit bin Soban sey isi tarah hadees bayan ki."
414,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney teen-teen baar aaza (ang) dho kar wuzu kiya aur isey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka amal qarar diya.
415,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen teen baar aaza (angon ko) dho kar wuzu kiya.
416,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney teen teen baar (aaza (angon ko) dho kar) wuzu kiya aur sar ka masah eik baar kiya."
417,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teen teen baar (wuzu ke angon ko dho kar) wuzu kartey they."
418,Hazrat Rabee binte Muawwiz ibne Ifraa (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah ney teen teen baar (aaza (angon ko) dho kar) wuzu kiya.
419,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik eik baar wuzu kiya aur farmaya : ye wo wuzu hai jis key baghair Allah Taala namaz qubul nahin farmata. phir do do baar wuzu kiya to farmaya : ye maqam aur martaba rakhney wala wuzu hai. aur teen teen baar wuzu kiya to farmaya : ye sab sey kamil wuzu hai. ye mera aur Hazrat Ibraheem Khaleelullah ka wuzu hai. jo shakhs is tarah wuzu karey phir farigh ho kar padhey : (أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ ، وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ) ""main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)  Allah key bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. to uskey liye jannat key aathon darwazey khul jatey hain jis mein sey wo chahey dakhil ho jaey."
420,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney pani talab farmaya aur eik eik baar wuzu kiya, phir farmaya : ye lazimi wuzu hai. ya farmaya : ye aisa wuzu hai ke jisney ye wuzu na kiya Allah uski namaz qubul nahin karta. phir do do baar wuzu kiya aur farmaya : jo shakhs ye wuzu kerega Allah usey dugna sawab dega. phir teen teen baar wuzu kiya aur farmaya : ye mera aur mujh sey pehley Rasulon ka wuzu hai."
421,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wuzu ka bhi eik shetan hai, jisey ""Walhaan"" kehtey hain, isliye pani key waswasey sey bacho."
422,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap sey wuzu key barey mein sawal kiya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey teen teen baar (aaza (angon ko) dho kar) wuzu kar key dikhaya, phir farmaya : wuzu ye hota hai, jisney is par izafa kiya, usney bura kiya, had sey tajawuz kiya (badhna) aur zulm kiya."
423,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main raat ko apni khaala (Ummul-momenin) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) key yahaan thehra. (raat ko) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uthey, aap ney eik mashk sey wuzu kiya aur wuzu bhi mukhtasar kiya (kam pani istimal kiya) main utha aur mainey bhi wesey hi kiya jaisey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kiya tha."
424,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik shakhs ko wuzu kartey dekha to farmaya : fuzul kharchi na karo, fuzul kharchi na karo."
425,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) wuzu kar rahey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) paas sey guzrey to farmaya : ye kya israaf (fuzul kharchi) hai? unhoney kaha : kya wuzu mein bhi israaf (fuzul kharch) hota hai? farmaya : haan, agar-che tum behtey darya par (uskey kinarey bethey) ho."
426,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khub kamil wuzu karney ka hukm diya."
427,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : kya main tumhen wo aa'maal na bataun jinki wajeh sey Allah Taala ghaltiyaan maaf farma deta hai aur nekiyon mein izafa farma deta hai? Sahaba ney arz kiya : kyon nahin ! Allah key Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is waqt kamil (sanwaar kar) wuzu karna jab (sardi waghera ki wajeh sey) dil na chahta ho, aur masjidon ki taraf ziyada qadam uthana, aur eik namaz key baad dusri namaz ka intizar karna."
428,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghaltiyon key kaffaarey ye hain is waqt kamil wuzu karna jab dil na chahta ho, aur masjidon ki taraf (chalney key liye) paon kaam mein lana aur namaz key baad namaz ka intizar karna."
429,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko daadhi Mubarak ka Khilal kartey dekha."
430,Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to daadhi Mubarak ka Khilal kiya.
431,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab wuzu kartey they to daadhi Mubarak ka Khilal kartey aur (khilal karney key liye) apni ungliyan kholtey, do baar aisa kartey."
432,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab wuzu kartey they to rukhsaaron key baalon ko thoda sa maltey they. phir daadhi mein nichey ki taraf ungliyan dal kar Khilal kartey they."
433,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney wuzu kiya to daadhi Mubarak ka Khilal kiya."
434,"Hazrat Amr bin Yahya apney walid sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney (apney walid) Amr bin Yahya key dada Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey arz kiya : kya aap mujhey (amali taur par) dikha saktey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kis tarah wuzu kartey they? Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : haan (abhi dikha deta hun.) unhoney pani talab farmaya , phir apney haathon par pani dal kar do baar haath dhoey. phir teen baar kulli ki aur naak saaf ki, phir teen baar chehra dhoya, phir kohniyon tak bazu do do baar dhoey, phir dono haathon sey sar ka masah kiya, (masaeh key doran mein) haathon ko aagey bhi laye aur peechhey bhi ley gaey. (masah karna) sar key agley hissey sey shuru kiya, phir guddi tak haathon ko ley gaey, phir wapis isi jagah ley aaye jahan sey shuru kiya tha. iskey baad dono paon dhoey."
435,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney wuzu kiya to sar ka masah eik hi baar kiya."
436,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sar ka masah eik baar kiya.
437,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney wuzu kiya to sar ka masah eik baar kiya."
438,"Hazrat Rabee binte Muawwiz ibne Ifra (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to do baar sar ka masah kiya."
439,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (wuzu key doran mein) kanon ka masah kiya. un ki andruni taraf ka masah shahadat ki ungliyon sey kiya aur angoothey kanon key bahar ki taraf ley aaye phir unka bahar aur andar sey masah kiya.
440,Hazrat Rabee (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to kanon key bahar aur andar masah kiya.
441,"Hazrat Rabee binte Muawwiz ibne Ifraa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to apney kanon key suraakhon mein ungliyan dakhil kin."
442,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to sar ka masah kiya, aur kanon ka bhi bahar andar sey masah kiya."
443,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaan sar mein shamil hain."
444,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaan sar mein shamil hain. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik baar sar ka masah kartey they aur aakhon key konon ka masah kartey they.
445,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaan sar ka hissa hain."
446,Hazrat Mustaurid bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to haath ki chhoti ungli sey apney dono qadmon ki ungliyon ka Khilal farmaya. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) Abul-Hasan Al-Qattan ney yehi riwayat apni sanad sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah bayan ki hai.
447,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to namaz key liye uthey to kamil wuzu kar, aur haathon aur paon ki ungliyon key darmiyan pani pahuncha."
448,Hazrat Aasim bin Laqeet bin Sabra apney walid sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kamil wuzu kar aur ungliyon mein Khilal kar.
449,Hazrat Abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab wuzu kartey they to apni angoothi ko harkat detey they (taa ke uskey nichey bhi pani pahunch jaey).
450,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh logon ko wuzu kartey dekha, (aap ney dekha ke jo afrad wuzu kar chukey they) un ki eidiyaan chamak rahi thin. (jo paon achchhi tarah na dhoney ki wajeh sey wazeh tor par khushk nazar aa rahi thin) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ediyon key liye aag ka azab hai, wuzu achchhi tarah mukammal karo."
451,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ediyon key liye aag ka azab hai."
452,"Hazrat abu-Salma (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney (apney bhai) Hazrat Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ko wuzu kartey dekha to farmaya : kamil wuzu kiya karo kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman suna hai : ediyon key liye aag ka azab hai."
453,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ediyon key liye aag ka azab hai.
454,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : ediyon (araqib) key liye aag ka azab hai."
455,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed , Hazrat Yazeed bin abu-Sufiyaan, Hazrat Sharjeel bin Hasna aur Hazrat Amr bin Aas Raziallahu anhum in sab sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : wuzu pura karo, ediyon key liye aag ka azab hai."
456,"Hazrat Abu-Haiya (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney wuzu kiya to apney dono qadam takhnon tak dhoey, phir farmaya : mainey chaha ke tum logon ko tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key wuzu ka tariqa (amali tor par) dikha dun."
457,Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to apney paon teen teen baar dhoey.
458,"Hazrat Rabee (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) merey paas tashrif laye aur mujh sey is hadees key mutalliq daryaft kiya, yani wo hadees jis mein unhoney zikr kiya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to paon dhoey (jab Hazrat Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) ney hadees bayan ki to) Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : log paon dhoney ka zikr kartey hain, mujhey to Quran Majeed mein sirf maseh ka zikr milta hai."
459,Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs is tarah mukammal wuzu karta hai jis tarah Allah ney hukm diya hai to uski farz namazein unkey darmiyani oqaat (waqt) key gunahon ka kaffara bin jati hain.
460,"Hazrat Rifaa bin Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bethey they to aap ney farmaya : kisi ki namaz us waqt tak mukammal nahin hoti jab tak wo apna wuzu is tarah kamil taur par na karey jis tarah usey Allah ney hukm diya hai. (yani) apna chehra aur kohniyon tak bazu dhoey, sar ka masah karey aur takhnon tak paon dhoey."
461,"Hazrat Hakam bin Sufiyan Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney wuzu kiya, phir pani ka eik chuloo ley kar apney sattar par chhidkaa."
462,"Hazrat Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hazrat Jibril (Alaihissalam) ney mujhey wuzu karney ka tariqa bataya, aur mujhey hukm diya ke main wuzu key baad aa janey waley peshab (key qatron key shubha sey bachney) key liye kapdey key nichey chheentey maar liya karun. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) abul-Hasan bin Salma ney ibne Labiaa key doosrey do shagirdon Abu Hatim aur Abdullah bin Yusuf Al Taneesi sey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
463,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to wuzu karey to (sharam gaah waley hissey key kapdey par) chheentey maar liya kar.
464,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to apney sattar par pani ki chheentey maarey.
465,"Hazrat Umme-Haani bint Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jis saal Makka Fateh huwa Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nahaney key pani ki taraf gaey, Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye parda taan diya (to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghusl farmaya), uskey baad aap ney apna kapda ley kar jism par lapet liya ."
466,"Hazrat Qais bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye, hamney aap key liye pani rakha to aap ney ghusl farmaya. hamney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko waras sey rangi hui eik chadar pesh ki to aap ney wo chadar odh li. (mujhey wo manzar is tarah yad hai) goya main (ab bhi) aap key pet Mubarak key shikan par waras ka nishan dekh raha hun ."
467,"Hazrat ummul-momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghusle-janabat kya to mainey aap ki khidmat mein kapda (tauliya waghera) pesh kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey wapis kar diya aur (jism par sey haath key sath) pani jhaadney lagey ."
468,"Hazrat Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kya, phir uskey baad jism Mubarak par pahna huwa ooni Jubba ulat kar us sey Chehrey Mubarak saaf kar liya."
469,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney wuzu kya aur khub achi tarah wuzu kya, phir teen baar yun kaha : (أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ وَحْدَہُ لَا شَرِیْکَ لَهُ ، وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ) 'main gawahi deta hun ke akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. uskey liye jannat key aathon darwazey khol diye jatey hain, wo jis mein sey chahey dakhil ho jaey . Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid (abul-Hasan bin Salma al-Qattan ney kaha ke Abu-Nuem key shagrid Ibrahim bin Nasar ney sabiqa riwayat ki misl bayan ki."
470,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi musalman wuzu karta hai aur wuzu bhi achcha karta hai, phir kehta hai : (أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ ، وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ) 'mein gawahi deta hun ke akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)  uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. uskey liye jannat key aathon darwazey khol diye jatey hain, wo jis mein sey chahey dakhil ho jaey ."
471,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye . hamney pital key eik bartan mein pani pesh kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey wuzu kya."
472,Hazrat ummul-mominin zeb bint Jahash (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unkey yahan pital ka eik tab huwa karta tha. unhoney farmaya : main is mein pani dal kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sar Mubarak mein kanghi kya karti thi .
473,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Tur ( eik qism key khuley munh key bartan) mein pani ley kar wuzu kya.
474,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) so jatey they yahan tak key kharratey leney lagtey, phir khadey ho kar namaz padhtey aur wuzu na kartey. Wakee bayan kartey hain ke ummul-momenin ki murad ye hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko baaz oqaat sajdey mein neend aa jati thi ."
475,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) so gaey yahan tak key kharratey leney lagey, phir uth khadey huye aur namaz padh li ."
476,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wo neend bethey bethey thi."
477,"Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aankhen peeth ka bandhan hain, lihaza jo shakhs so jaey, usey chahiye ke wuzu kerey."
478,"Hazrat Safwan bin Assaal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen hukm detey they ke hum teen din tak apney mozey na utaaren siwaye iskey ke janabat ki wajeh sey (ghusl karna padey. tab to utaarna hi padengey) lekin peshaab, pakhaney ya neend ki wajeh sey (mozey utaarney ki zarurat nahin.)"
479,Hazrat Busra bint Safwan (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs apni sharamgaah ko haath lagaey to usey chahiye ke wuzu kerey.
480,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs apney uzue-khaas ko haath lagaey to is par lazim hai ke wuzu kerey."
481,"Hazrat ummul-mominin Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : jo shakhs apney uzue-tanasul ko haath lagaey , usey chahiye ke wuzu kerey."
482,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : jo shakhs apni sharmgah ko haath lagaey , to usey chahiye ke wuzu kerey."
483,"Hazrat Qais bin Talaq Hanfi apney walid (Hazrat Talaq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : mainey suna ke kisi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey uzue-khaas ko haath laganey key barey mein sawal kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is sey wuzu lazim nahin aata , wo bhi tera eik hissa hai.'"
484,Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey uzue-khaas ko chhuney key barey mein sawal kya gaya to aap ney farmaya : wo to terey jism ka eik tukda hai.
485,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis chiz mein aag tabdili kar dey , us (key khaney ki wajeh) sey wuzu karo . Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : kya main garm pani (pi kar uski wajeh) sey bhi wuzu karun? Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : bhatijey ! jab tum Rasoolullah ki koi hadees suno , to misalen na bayan kya karo ."
486,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis chiz ko aag ney chhua ho, us (key khaney peeney ki wajeh) sey wuzu karo ."
487,"Hazrat Yazeed bin abu-Malik (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki ke wo apney haath apney kanon par rakh kar farmatey they : (ye kaan) behrey ho jaeyn, agar mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey na suna ho : jis chiz ko aag ney chhua ho, uski wajeh sey wuzu karo ."
488,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (bakri key) shaaney ka gosht khaya, phir apney haath us taat sey saaf kar liye jo aapkey nichey bicha huwa tha, phir aap namaz key liye khadey huye aur namaz ada ki."
489,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney roti gosht khaya aur wuzu na kya."
490,"Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main ( khalifa) Waleed ya (khalifa) Abdul-Malik key sath raat key khaney par mojud tha. jab namaz ka waqt huwa to main wuzu karney key liye uth khada huwa . to Hazrat Jaafar bin Amr bin Umayya ney farmaya : main apney walid (Hazrat Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) key barey mein gawahi deta hun ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key barey mein gawahi di ke aap ney aag sey tayyar shuda khana khaya , aur phir naya wuzu kiye baghair namaz ada farmaai. (is par) Hazrat Ali bin Abdullah bin Abbas ney farmaya : main bhi apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ) key barey mein yehi gawahi deta hun ."
491,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bakri key kandhey ka gosht pesh kya gaya . aap ney is mein sey khaya , phir namaz padhi aur pani ko haath bhi na lagaya ."
492,"Hazrat Suwed bin Noman Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Sahaba Raziallahu anhum Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath khaibar ki taraf ( jihad key liye) rawana huye . jab wo maqam Sehba par pahunchey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Asr ki namaz ada ki phir khana talab farmaya to aap ki khidmat mein sirf sattu pesh kiye gaey (aur koi chiz mojud nahin thi), sab ney khaya piya. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney pani talab farmaya aur kulli ki, phir khadey ho kar hamen maghrib ki namaz padhaai."
493,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bakri key shaaney ka gosht khaya , phir kulli ki, haath dhoey aur namaz ada ki."
494,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey oont key gosht sey wuzu ka masla daryaft kya gaya to aap ney farmaya : is sey wuzu karo ."
495,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke oont ka gosht kha kar wuzu karen, aur bhed bakri ka gosht kha kar wuzu na karen."
496,"Hazrat Usaid bin Huzer (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bakriyon ka doodh pi kar wuzu na karo, aur oonton ka doodh pi kar wuzu karo."
497,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : oonton ka gosht kha kar wuzu karo, bakriyon ka gosht kha kar wuzu na karo, aur oontniyon ka doodh pi kar wuzu karo, bakriyon ka doodh pi kar wuzu na karo aur bakriyon key baadey mein namaz padh liya karo, oonton key baadey mein namaz na padho ."
498,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : doodh pi kar kulli kar liya karo kyonkey is mein chiknaahat hoti hai.'"
499,"Hazrat ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum doodh piyo to kulli kar liya karo, kyonkey is mein chiknaahat hoti hai."
500,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : doodh pi kar kulli kar liya karo kyonkey is mein chiknaahat hoti hai.
501,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik bakri doh kar doodh piya , phir pani mangwaya kar kulli ki aur farmaya : is mein chiknaahat hoti hai."
502,"Janab Urwa Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey hain unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni eik biwi ka bosa liya , phir namaz key liye tashrif ley gaey, aur wuzu nahin kya. ( Urwa kehtey hain) mainey kaha : wo zarur aap hi hongi to aap hans din."
503,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wuzu kartey , phir bosa letey aur (dobara) wuzu kiye baghair namaz padh letey , aur baaz oqaat aap merey sath bhi ye kartey ."
504,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mazi key mutalliq sawal kya gaya to aap ney farmaya : is sey wuzu hai aur mani sey ghusl hai."
505,"Hazrat miqdaad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey daryaft kya ke agar mard apni biwi key qarib jaey aur inzaal na ho (to kya hukm hai?) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ko ye soorate-hal pesh aaye to wo apni sharmgah par pani dal ley, yani istinja kar ley aur wuzu kar ley."
506,"Hazrat Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey mazi ki wajeh sey bahut mashaqqat bardasht kerni padti thi (kyonkey) main uski wajeh sey bahut kasrat sey (baar baar) ghusl karta tha. chunanche mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey daryaft kya to aap ney farmaya : tujhey us sey wuzu kafi hai. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! jo merey kapdey ko lag jaey uska kya karun? farmaya : tujhey pani ka eik chullu kafi hai. jahan tera khayal hai ke wo lag gaee hai wahan (chullu bhar pani) chhidak dey."
507,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke wo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) key yahan gaey . wo ( ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye. (baat cheet key doran Hazrat Ubai ney) farmaya : mujhey mazi aa gaee thi to mainey uzue-khaas ko dho kar wuzu kya hai. ( isliye bahar aaney mein der hui) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kya ye ( wuzu kar lena) kafi hota hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan . farmaya : kya aap ney ye masla Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (khud) suna hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan .
508,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko uth kar baitulkhalaa tashrif ley gaey aur zaruri hajat sey farigh huye. phir Chehrey Mubarak aur dono haath dhoey aur so gaey. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : hamein abu-Bakar bin Khallad Baahli ney yahyaa bin Saeed sey , unhoney Shoba sey , unhoney Salma bin Kuheil sey unhoney Bakeer sey , unhoney Kureb sey , unhoney ibne-Abbas key wastey sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi ki jaisi riwayat bayan ki."
509,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) har namaz key liye wuzu kiya kartey they, jabke hum log tamam namazein eik wuzu sey padh liya kartey they."
510,"Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Barida (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) har namaz key liye (naya) wuzu kiya kartey they. jis din Makka Fateh huwa , us din aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sab namazein eik hi wuzu sey ada farmaaeen."
511,"Hazrat Fazal bin Mubashshir (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) ko eik wuzu sey kaee namazein padhtey dekha. (Hazrat Fazal ney farmaya :) mainey kaha : aap ney ye kya kiya? unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha tha, chunanche main bhi wesay hi karta hun jis tarah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kiya tha."
512,"Hazrat abu-Ghutef Hazli (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main masjid mein Hazrat Abdullah bin umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhuma) ki majlis mein unkey irshadat sun raha tha. jab namaz ka waqt huwa to unhoney uth kar wuzu kiya aur namaz padhi , phir apni jagah par aa bethey , phir jab Asr ki namaz ka waqt huwa to aap ney uth kar wuzu kiya, namaz padhi , aur phir apni jagah par aa bethey . phir jab maghrib ki namaz ka waqt huwa to aap ney uth kar wuzu kiya, namaz padhi , phir apni jagah tashrif ley aaye. mainey arz kya : Allah Taala aap ko salaamat rakhey (ye irshad farmaiye ke) har namaz key liye wuzu karna farz hai ya sunnat? unhoney farmaya : tum ney mera ye amal mehsus kar liya? mainey kaha : ji haan. unhoney farmaya : nahin (ye farz nahin hai), agar main subah ki namaz key liye wuzu karun to uskey sath sab namazein padh sakta hun jab tak wuzu na tootey. baat ye hai ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshade Mubarak suna hai : jo shakhs paak (baa-wuzoo) honey key bawajud wuzu karta hai usey das nekiyan milti hain. aur main bhi nekiyon ki raghbat (dichaspi) rakhta hun."
513,"Janab Ibaad bin Tameem (Rahimahullah) apney chacha Hazrat Abdullah bin Yazeed bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya gaya ke agar koi aadmi namaz mein kuchh mehsus karey (usey shak padey ke hawa khaarij hui hai to kya kerey)?  to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin (wuzu karney na jaey) yahan tak key boo mehsus karey ya aawaz suney."
514,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey namaz mein) wuzu tootney ka shubha paida honey key barey mein sawal kiya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz chhod kar na jaey yahan tak key aawaz suney ya boo mehsus karey."
515,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aawaz ya boo key baghair wuzu (dobara karna zaruri) nahin hota.
516,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Amr bin Ata (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Saaib bin Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke apna kapda soongh rahey they, mainey arz ki : iski kya wajeh hai? unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : wuzu (wajib) nahin hai magar aawaz ki wajeh sey ya boo ki wajeh sey."
517,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sehra mein mojud pani (key qudrati taalaabon) key barey mein puchha gaya jin sey chopaey aur darindey pani peetey hon. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab pani ki miqdaar do matkon key barabar ho jaey to koi chiz usey napak nahin karti. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Muhammad bin Is-haq key doosrey shagrid Abdullah bin Mubarak key wastey sey isi tarah ki riwayat bayan ki."
518,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab pani do ya teen matkey ho to usey koi chiz napak nahin karti. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) Abu-Hasan bin Salma Qataan ney yehi riwayat apni aali sanad sey , yani ba-wasta Abu Hatim aur Abu-Waleed waghera, Hammad sey Imam Ibne-Maja key wastey key baghair bayan ki hai."
519,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey Makka aur Madina key darmiyan (raastey mein) waqey un hauzon key mutalliq daryaft kiya gaya jin sey darindey, kuttey aur gadhey pani pi jatey hain, kya un (key pani) sey paakizgi hasil ki ja sakti hai (wuzu aur ghusl waghera kiya ja sakta hai)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo kuchh unhoney apney peton mein dal liya, wo unka hai aur jo (pani) bach gaya, wo hamarey liye paak karney wala hai."
520,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log (safar key doran mein) eik taalaab par pahunchey, dekha to us main eik gadhey ki laash padi thi. hamney us sey (pani leney sey) ijtinab kiya (bache) yahan tak key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif ley aaye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pani ko koi chiz naapak nahin karti. chunanche hamney pani piya, (janweron ko) pilaya , aur (mishkeezon waghera mein) sath ley liya."
521,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pani ko koi chiz napak nahin karti siwaye iskey jo uski boo, zaiqey ya rang par ghalib aa jaey."
522,"Hazrat Lubaaba binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki god mein peshab kar diya. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! apna kapda mujhey dijiye aur khud koi aur kapda pehan lijiye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ladkey key peshab sey to chheentey maarey jatey hain aur ladki key peshab ki wajeh sey (kapda) dhoya jata hai."
523,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein eik (doodh pine wala) bacha laya gaya. usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (key kapdon) par peshab kar diya, aap ney wahan pani chhidak diya aur kapda dhoya nahin."
524,"Hazrat Umme Qais binte Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein apna eik (doodh pine wala) bachcha ley kar hazir hui jo (abhi) khana nahin khata tha. usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (key kapron) par peshab kar diya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney pani mangwaya aur is par chhidak diya."
525,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney doodh pine wale bachche key peshab key barey mein farmaya : ladkey key peshab par pani chhidkaa jata hai aur ladki ka peshab dhoya jata hai. Abul-Hasan bin Salma ney kaha , hamein Ahmed bin Musa ney, in ko Abu Yamaan misri ney bayan kiya ke mainey Imam Shafai (Rahimahullah) sey is hadeese nabawi key mutalliq sawal kiya (jis mein ye hukm hai ke),  ladkey key peshab par pani chhidkaa jaey aur ladki key peshab sey kapda dhoya jaey. (mainey puchha is farq ki kya wajeh hai jabkey) dono peshab eik hi chiz hain? Imam Shafai (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : iski wajeh ye hai ke ladkey ka peshab pani aur mitti sey hai aur ladki ka peshab gosht aur khoon sey hai. phir kaha samajh gaey? mainey kaha : ji nahin (main nahin samjha) farmaya : Allah Taala ney jab Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida kiya to (unhen mitti aur pani sey paida kiya aur) Hawwa (Alaihissalam) un ki chhoti pasli sey paida hui. goya ladkey ka peshab pani aur mitti sey wajood mein aaya hai (jis sey Adam (Alaihissalam) baney they) aur ladki ka peshab gosht aur khoon sey (jis sey Hawwa (Alaihissalam) ki paidaish hui) ab samajh gaey? mainey kaha : ji haan. unhoney farmaya : Allah tujhey is (ilm aur samajh) sey faeyda dey."
526,"Hazrat Abu-Samah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khaadim huwa karta tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein Hazrat Hasan ya Hazrat Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) ko laya gaya, (wo us waqt doodh peetey bachey they), unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key seene Mubarak par peshab kar diya. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney dhona chaha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pani chhidak do kyonkey ladki ka peshab dhoya jata hai aur ladkey key peshab sey pani chhidkaa jata hai."
527,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib , Umme Kurz sey bayan kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ladkey key peshab par pani chhidkaa jata hai aur ladki ka peshab dhoya jata hai."
528,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik baddoo ney masjid mein peshab kar diya. kuchh log (usey rokney key liye) uski taraf bhaagey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uska peshab band na karo. phir pani ka eik dol mangwaya aur is par baha diya."
529,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (masjid mein) tashrif farma they ke eik baddoo masjid mein aaya. usney kaha : aey Allah ! mujhey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bakhsh dey aur hamarey sath kisi aur ki bakhshish na karna. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hans padey aur farmaya : tu ney eik wasee (badi) chiz (rehmate Ilaahi) ko mehdood kar diya. phir wo  (ea'raab) (dehaati) wapis palta. abhi masjid hi key eik hissey mein tha ke (khada ho kar) paon eik doosrey sey door kar key peshab karney laga. usi Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ney Deen ki samajh aa janey key baad (apna waqia bayan kartey huye) farmaya : merey maa baap aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par qurban hon ! aap uth kar merey paas aaye, mujhey na daantaa, na bura bhala kaha, bas ye farmaya : ye masjid aisi jagah hai ke is mein peshab nahin kiya jata, ye to Allah key zikr aur namaz key liye taamir ki gaee hai. phir aap ney pani ka dol talab farmaya jo peshab par baha diya gaya."
530,"Hazrat Waasila Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney bayan kiya ke eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa , usney kaha : aey Allah ! mujh par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par rehmat farma aur hum par nazil honey wali apni rehmat mein kisi aur ko shareek na karna. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : afsos ! tu ney la-mahdood ko mehdud kar diya. Sahaba kehtey hain : wo ea'raab (dehaati) taangein khol kar peshab karney laga. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : ruk, ruk. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey chhod do. phir pani ka eik dol mangwa kar us jagah baha diya."
531,"Hazrat Ibrahim bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ki eik londi sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biwi Ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey masla puchha aur kaha : main aurat hun, (qamis ka) daman lamba rakhti hun (jo chaltey waqt zamin sey chhuta hai) mera guzar gandi jagah sey bhi hota hai (to kya main daman dhoya karun)? Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha , Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey baad wali (paak) zamin paak kar deti hai."
532,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke kisi ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum masjid ki taraf aatey hain to raastey mein napaak jagah par bhi paon padta hai (hum kya keren)? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zamin ka eik hissa doosrey hisse (sey hasil honey wali najasat sey jootey ya qadam) ko paak kar deta hai.
533,"qabila banu Abdul-Ash'hal ki eik khatoon (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey masla poochha, mainey kaha : merey (ghar) aur masjid key darmiyan raasta gandaa (aur koodey karkat wala) hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uskey baad saaf raasta bhi hai? mainey kaha : ji haan, farmaya : is sey uski bharpaai ho jaeygi."
534,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Madina ki galiyon mein sey kisi gali mein un ki mulaqat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey hui aur wo us waqt junbi (samhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein) they. wo khamoshi sey chaley gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki adam mojudgi ko mehsus farmaya. jab wo aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! tum kahan (chaley gaey) they? unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! jab aap mujh sey miley to main junbi (samhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein) tha. mujhey achcha na laga ke nahaaey baghair aap key paas bethun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin napaak nahin hota.
535,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey meri mulaqat hui jabke main haalate janabat (samhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein) mein tha to main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey alag ho gaya aur ghusl kiya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhen kya huwa tha ke mujh sey alag ho gaey? mainey kaha : main junbi (samhog ke bad naapaaki ki haalat mein) tha , Allah key Rasool ney farmaya : yaqinan musalman napaak nahin hota."
536,"Janab Amr bin Memun (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) sey sawal kiya ke agar kapdey ko mani lag jaey to kya hum sirf usi hissey ko dho lein ya pura kapda dhoein? Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey ko bhi wo chiz lag jati thi to hum kapdey ko dho kar usey utaar detey they, phir wohi kapda pehan kar namaz padhney tashrif ley jatey, aur mujhey kapdey mein dhoney ka nishan nazar aa raha hota tha."
537,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : baaz oqaat main us chiz ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey par sey khud apney haath sey khurachti thi."
538,"Hazrat Hamaam bin Haris (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key yahan eik mehman aa gaya. unhoney (raat ko soney key liye) usey eik zard lihaaf dilwa diya. usey ehtilaam ho gaya. (subah key waqt) usey is baat sey sharam mehsus hui ke wo kapda is haal mein (Ummul-mominin key paas) bhejey ke is mein ehtilaam ka nishan ho. usney lihaaf pani mein dubo kar (geelaa kar key)  bhej diya (taake sara lihaaf geelaa honey ki wajeh sey wo nishan nazar na aaye, sirf mutaassira hissey ko dhona kaafi na samjha). Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : usney hamara kapda kyon kharab kar diya? (ab ye itna mota kapda kab khushk hoga?) agar wo usey ungli sey khurch daalta to kafi hota. main bhi baaz oqaat (kabhi kabhi) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey sey ye chiz apni ungli sey khurch diya karti thi."
539,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : baaz oqaat mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key kapdey par wo chiz nazar aati to main usey khurch kar utaar deti thi."
540,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney apni hamsheera (behan), yani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mutahra (paak biwi) Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kiya : kya Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us kapdey mein namaz padh letey they jis mein sohbat ki hoti? unhoney kaha : haan, agar is mein napaaki ka asar na hota."
541,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye aur aap key sar sey pani tapak raha tha. aap ney eik hi kapda zeb tan (pehan) kar key hamein namaz padhaai jabke aap ney uskey dono kinarey mukhalif simton mein dal rakhey they. jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey farigh huye to umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap hamein eik kapda odh kar namaz padha detey hain? farmaya : haan, main is ko pehan kar namaz padh leta hun, agar-che usey pehan kar mubashrat (sambhog) bhi ki ho."
542,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya : kisi ney biwi key paas jatey waqt jo kapda pehan rakha ho, kya wohi pehan kar namaz padh sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan, agar is mein koi chiz nazar aaye (jo dhoney key laaiq ho) to usey dho ley."
543,"Hazrat Hamaam bin Haris sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney peshab kiya. uskey baad wuzu kiya aur mozon par masah kiya. unhein kaha gaya : aap bhi ye kaam kartey hain? farmaya : mujhey kya rukawat hai (mein kyon na karun)? jabke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is tarah kartey dekha hai. Ibrahim ney kaha : logon ko Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees bahut pasand aai kyonkey wo sura Maeyda key nazil honey key baad Islam laye they."
544,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya aur mozon par masah kiya.
545,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) key liye tashrif ley gaey. Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) eik bartan mein pani ley kar aap key sath gaey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) sey farigh ho kar wuzu kiya aur mozon par masah kiya.
546,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko mozon par masah kartey dekha to farmaya : kya aap log is tarah kartey hain (masah kar letey hain, paon nahin dhotey)? uskey baad Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas dono ki baham (aapas mein) mulaqat ho gaee to Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : merey bhatijey (ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma)) ko mozon par maseh ka masla bata dijiye. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath hotey they aur mozon par masah kar liya kartey they, is mein koi harj nahin samajhtey they. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : agar-che koi qazaey-hajat (peshaab-paakhaane) sey farigh ho kar aaya ho? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : haan (tab bhi masah kar letey they)."
547,Hazrat Sehal Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mozon par masah kiya aur hamen bhi mozon par masah karney ka hukm diya.
548,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik safar mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kuchh pani hai? phir aap ney wuzu kiya aur mozon par masah kiya. phir lashkar sey aa miley aur unhen namaz padhaai."
549,"Hazrat ibne Barida apney walid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Najaashi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein do saada siyah mozey tohfe key tor par bheje. aap ney unhen pahnaa, phir wuzu kiya aur un par masah kiya."
550,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mozey key ooper bhi masah kiya aur nichey bhi.
551,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jo wuzu kar raha tha aur (paaon dhoney key bajaey paon mein pehney huye) mozey dho raha tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (usey mutawajjeh karney key liye) haath sey usey (halka sa) dhakela aur farmaya : mujhey masah karney ka hukm diya gaya hai.  aur (uski wazahat kartey huye) apney haathon ko (paon ki) ungliyon sey shuru kar key pindli key shuru tak ley gaey aur ungliyon sey (goya) khat kheenchey."
552,"Hazrat Shureh bin Hani (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey mozon par maseh ka masla puchha to unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas jao kyonkey unhen ye masla mujh sey ziyada malum hai. main Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur un sey masah key barey mein daryaft kiya. unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein maseh ka hukm diya kartey they. muqeem key liye eik din raat aur musafir key liye teen din."
553,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney musafir key liye teen din ki muddat muqarrar farmaai hai, lekin agar saail mazeed muddat key liye ijazat maangta to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) paanch din ki bhi ijazat dey detey."
554,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musafir key liye mozon par maseh ki muddat teen din hai. ghaaliban ye bhi farmaya : aur teen raat."
555,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Sahaba kiram ney arz kiya, aey Allah key Rasool ! mozey pehan kar wuzu ka kya hukm hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musafir key liye teen din raat, aur muqeem key liye eik din raat (masah karna durust hai)."
556,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney musafir ko ijazat di ke jab wo wuzu kar key mozey pehney, phir naya wuzu karey to teen din raat tak masah karey, aur muqeem key liye eik din raat (masah karney ki ijazat di)."
557,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Imaara (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai aur ye wo Sahabi hain jinkey ghar mein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dono qiblon ki taraf munh kar key namaz padhi hai (qibla tabdeel honey ka hukm nazil honey sey pehley Islam laye they). unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : kya main mozon par masah kar liya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan, unhoney kaha : eik din? (phir) kaha : do din? (phir) kaha : teen din? yahan tak key saat din tak ja pahunchey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey kaha : jab tak tumhara ji chahey."
558,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Misr sey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas (Madina Munawwara) aaye. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney puchha : tum ney kitni muddat sey mozey nahin utarey? unhoney kaha : Juma sey Juma tak (hafta bhar) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tum ney sunnat key mutabiq amal kiya.
559,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya aur juraabon aur jooton par masah kiya.
560,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kiya aur juraabon aur jooton par masah kiya. (Esa bin Yunus key shagrid) Muallaa bin Mansoor ney apni hadees mein kaha ke merey ilm main to ye hai ke unhoney sirf  ""والنعلین"" hi kaha."
561,Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mozon par aur sar key kapdey par masah kiya.
562,"Hazrat Jaafar bin Amr apney walid (Hazrat Amr bin Hures Makhzoomi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko mozon aur pagdi par masah kartey dekha hai."
563,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sohaan key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Abu-Muslim (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) key sath tha. unhoney eik aadmi ko dekha ke wo wuzu karney key liye mozey utaar raha hai. Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ney us sey farmaya : mozon par, amaamey aur sar key agley hissey par masah kar lo, kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko mozon par aur sar key kapdey par masah kartey dekha hai."
564,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kya aur aap ney Qatar ka bana huwa amama pehna huwa tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney amama key nichey haath dal kar sar key agley hissey ka masah kiya aur amama Mubarak ko khola nahin."
